Attempts to create a self supporting enclosed environment have always failed in the past. It makes sense to reduce travel time as much asw possible. We don't want the first manned interplanetary mission to become our first interplanetary manned disaster.  <p>~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
